properties.property: local spawn_rate = 5 self.prng = self.prng or love.math.newRandomGenerator(0xFACADA) self.bias = self.bias or 0.5 self.timer = (self.timer or 0) + dt if self.timer >= spawn_rate then self.timer = self.timer - spawn_rate local l, t, r, b = gamecamera:getBoundaries() if self.prng:random() < self.bias then self.bias = self.bias - 0.25 local near = gameroom:chooseFromGroup('player', function(a, b) return a.x < b.x end) local properties = { direction = 'right', move_speed = 65 + self.prng:random(10) } gameroom:addInstance('undead', 'objects', l, near.y_land, properties) else self.bias = self.bias + 0.25 local near = gameroom:chooseFromGroup('player', function(a, b) return a.x > b.x end) local properties = { direction = 'left', move_speed = 45 + self.prng:random(10) } gameroom:addInstance('undead', 'objects', r, near.y_land, properties) end end
